schemas.name: User.gql
schemas.content:
type User {
  id: Int!
  email: String
  verifiedEmail: Boolean!
  firstName: String!
  lastName: String!
  age: Int
  password: String
  phoneNumber: String
  verifiedPhoneNumber: Boolean!
  profilePhoto: String
  fullname: String
  isDriving: Boolean!
  isRiding: Boolean!
  isTaken: Boolean!
  lastLng: Float
  lastLat: Float
  lastOrientation: Float
  createdAt: String!
  updatedAt: String
}

type Query {
  user: User
}
